      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_5633717911656846451.png",
                "id": "talent69712",
                "key": "Rain of Stone",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rain of Stone"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Stone Stele</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/bd88dd4e84f0956abd3d34b19442d2c6_6986498545420954992.png",
                "id": "talent56597",
                "key": "Dominus Lapidis",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dominus Lapidis"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span>, memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Stone Stele</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Jade Shield</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Jade Shield</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p>Menyediakan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Perisai</span> untuk Karakter Aktif-mu.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/857631feb4f9832ee5644c9f6faf3a44_3928146373456003602.png",
                "id": "talent78930",
                "key": "Dominus Lapidis: Striking Stone",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dominus Lapidis: Striking Stone"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>. Memberikan status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Petrification</span> kepada Karakter target.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Petrification</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Karakter tidak dapat menggunakan Skill.</span></p><p>(Berlangsung hingga Ronde ini berakhir)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/c701cbbd15b971aaee458b19e71b4ced_1395076569667719475.png",
                "id": "talent63380",
                "key": "Planet Befall",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Planet Befall"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5493689117464295876.png",
                "id": "talent5941",
                "key": "Stone Stele",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/905fb3dd007f1806491f7e9df8812d45_257570629695455159.png",
                "title": "Stone Stele"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_2183752982482155759.png",
                "id": "talent6533",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Perisai</span></strong></p><p>Saat Karakter yang dilindungi Perisai menerima DMG, Perisai akan terkonsumsi untuk menahan DMG yang diterima.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3315240828906697240.png",
                "id": "talent60015",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
